tweakPrompt: Lägg till en slide med finansiell jämförelse mot föregående år

input.query:
SELECT 
  year,
  revenue,
  profit,
  employees,
  equity_ratio,
  profit_margin
FROM company_financials
WHERE organization_number = '556399-7146'
  AND year IN (2023, 2024)
ORDER BY year

SELECT *
FROM company_financials
WHERE organization_number = '556399-7146'
LIMIT 5

SELECT column_name, data_type 
FROM information_schema.columns 
WHERE table_name = 'company_financials'
ORDER BY ordinal_position

SELECT 
  bokslutsaar,
  omsattning,
  resultat,
  anstallda,
  soliditet,
  rorelsemarginal,
  lonsamhetsindex,
  eget_kapital
FROM company_financials
WHERE org_nummer = '556399-7146'
  AND bokslutsaar IN (2023, 2024)
ORDER BY bokslutsaar

SELECT 
  bokslutsaar,
  omsattning,
  resultat,
  anstallda,
  soliditet,
  rorelsemarginal,
  lonsamhetsindex,
  eget_kapital
FROM company_financials
WHERE org_nummer LIKE '%556399-7146%'
ORDER BY bokslutsaar DESC
LIMIT 5
